txt.en: 'Fool! Interloper! You come at the behest of a dying man to do what he could not! For what?'
'Come then, if you must! Know this! This all for naught!'
'The old fool tricked us all! There is nothing in his haversack. No riches.'
'His vengeance is all there is. Now, it has lead you to what will become your tomb, or ours.'
'Fate placed us here together and so we end this sordid tale! Get them!'
'Hilâma, no! You will pay for that!'
